# Session orchestrator

**Fresh hub / bootstrap** → `./scripts/repos-status.sh` then `.cursor/skills/bootstrap-hub/SKILL.md` (agent asks for repos if missing).

**Start work** / `/start-work` → load `.cursor/skills/session-orchestrator/SKILL.md`. You run `./scripts/*`.

**Workflow** / `/workflow` → load `.cursor/skills/workflow-orchestrator/SKILL.md`. Resume from `workflow.json` phase; do not restart from chat history.

**`/workflow status`** → same skill; one-screen status from `workflow.json`.

**`accept brief`** / **`accept`** → workflow gate 1 (phase `brief_review`).

**`accept plan`** → workflow gate 2 → `./scripts/workflow-accept-plan.sh <codename>`.

**`reopen brief`** / **`reopen plan`** → `workflow-reopen-brief.py` / `workflow-reopen-plan.py`.

**End session** / `/end-session` → load `.cursor/skills/session-end/SKILL.md`.

**Template version / upgrade hub** → load `.cursor/skills/hub-upgrade/SKILL.md`. Run `./scripts/hub-status.sh` first; upgrade only when user says so.
